ZH: 我不小心踩到了一根香蕉皮。
EN: I accidentally stepped on a banana peel.

ZH: 他不小心踩到了一个坑里。
EN: He accidentally stepped into a hole.

ZH: 我经过花坛时踩断了一株花。
EN: I accidentally stepped on a flower while passing by the flowerbed.

ZH: 小狗一不小心踩到了我的脚。
EN: The puppy accidentally stepped on my foot.

ZH: 他在沙滩上踩到了一片贝壳。
EN: He stepped on a seashell at the beach.

ZH: 路上有人踩了一张纸。
EN: Someone stepped on a piece of paper on the road.

ZH: 孩子们在草地上踩来踩去。
EN: The children are stepping on and off the grassland.

ZH: 她穿了一双舒适的鞋子，免得踩痛脚。
EN: She wore a comfortable pair of shoes to avoid stepping on her feet.

ZH: 请不要踩坏草坪。
EN: Please do not step on the lawn.

ZH: 当你过马路时，一定要注意不要被车踩到。
EN: When crossing the road, be sure not to be run over by a car.

ZH: 她的发展机会被同事踩在了脚下。
EN: Her career opportunities were trampled upon by her colleagues.

ZH: 小偷踩着亮度调暗的楼梯逃走了。
EN: The thief made his escape by stepping on the darkened stairs.

ZH: 如果你踩在这个按钮上，火警将会被触发。
EN: If you step on this button, the fire alarm will be triggered.

ZH: 他踩着节拍跳舞。
EN: He danced to the rhythm.

ZH: 小猫玩得太起劲，踩痛了我的脚。
EN: The kitten played too vigorously and stepped on my foot.

ZH: 她踩在高跟鞋上优雅地走过舞池。
EN: She gracefully walked through the dance floor on high heels.

ZH: 我们将踩踏着这片狭窄的山路前进。
EN: We will proceed by stepping on this narrow mountain path.

ZH: 他骑自行车踩得很快。
EN: He pedals the bicycle very quickly.

ZH: 她踩着踏板演奏了一首很动听的曲子。
EN: She played a beautiful melody on the pedal.

ZH: 他专心致志地踩着高低不平的石子上山。
EN: He climbed the uneven stones focused and determined.
